 />\n黃楚標安排退休後住深圳送裝修<br />\n坐富豪私人飛機遊泰國日本<br />\n收新鴻基一部二手跑步機<br />\n無申報<br />\n<br />\n<strong>公職人員行為失當判監20個月，後來減到12個月</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>許仕仁：</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n上任前收取850萬<br />\n<br />\n法官判詞指，許仕仁一旦收取850萬，在職期間的獨立性將徹底被削弱，無法恰當地履行公職<br />\n<br />\n<strong>公職人員行為失當等判監7年半</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>梁振英：</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n上任前收取UGL 5000萬<br />\n無申報<br />\n<br />\n<strong>廉署調查後諮詢律政司意見，證據不足不起訴</strong>「由於梁振英沒有利益衝突，因此沒有法律規定需要申報他在成為行政長官之前，與UGL所簽訂協議而會獲得款項的金額。故此，沒有申報並不構成任何公職人員行為失當罪」<br />\n<br />\n叫曾蔭權同許仕仁情何以堪呢～<br />\n<br />\n轉載林彥邦fb"},{"pid":"81048854145943c4ba4c4af6d54a49083ad6cace","tid":938754,"uid":220853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:23:25.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 太空空氣清新機"},{"pid":"f603403fb0783a82336e55d83338482ada0b757e","tid":938754,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4690be21f01fa9793654bc54ba8d25b65ff6c62","tid":938754,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T16:54:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vpbvij.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vpbvij.png&h=e606046e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b98ab280c79ab73bb528933b95a76dd2a1324b4d","tid":938754,"uid":77143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"87891e78fa1e995590af83d727cd3e14aa93df41","tid":938754,"uid":157453,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"過多幾年，曾蔭權要上神臺了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:26:30.000Z","msg":"擊退索羅斯嘅曾蔭權從來都係神檯度"},{"pid":"2677a6a0ebde0f83086a2bde9fb966de022d97b2","tid":938754,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T17:28:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}